    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "万历",
        "内监",
        "孙安"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（万历、四内监同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金龙盘玉桂，凤凰叩九霄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前殿角九龙出水，后殿角紧靠花园。金钟打罢玉鼓吹，众文武三呼万岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，孤万历，至我登基以来，风调雨顺，国泰民安，枪刀入库，马放南山，真"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乃清平世界。今乃大朝之日。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "内臣，闪放龙门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "内监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闪放龙门。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙安上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为国忠良比，方显正忠臣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣孙安参见吾皇。万岁万岁万万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙爱卿，你也来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙爱卿上殿，有何本奏？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣本奏张居正。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙爱卿，你可有多大官职？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣官居刑科给事中之职。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你官居给事中之职，你就敢参奏阁老，倘然猛虎回头，打你一掌，那是怎了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你府下可有多少家眷？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣一十八口。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回府造来一十八口棺匣，再来奏我那张爱卿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣遵旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金殿领王旨，回府造棺匣。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙安下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "内臣，殿下有事无事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "内监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无事。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卷帘朝散。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
