    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "万历",
        "上写着云南道居官不浅",
        "众人",
        "内监",
        "夫人",
        "孙安",
        "家院",
        "张居正",
        "徐彦昭",
        "我今不打万历主",
        "我把铜锤拿在手",
        "杨太",
        "杨溥",
        "职都押在龙书案",
        "马子千"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（夫人上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷在朝作忠臣，荣华富贵从天降。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙安上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下朝回来，对夫人细说明白。"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷往日下的朝来，欢天喜地的；今日下的朝，为何愁眉不展？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人不知。是我今天上的朝去，本参张居正，万岁恼怒，言说你府下可有多少"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家眷？是我言道，臣一十八口。万岁言道，回府造来一十八口棺匣，再来奏我"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那张爱卿。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（家院上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请下能工巧匠，造下一十九口，内有一口，长只一尺，宽只七寸，二龙戏珠，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄纱罩顶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（家院下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷，造下那一口棺匣，却是何意？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人，那昏王听我本奏，还则罢了，若要不肯，他就丧在那口棺匣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷，那不欺了君了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你妇道家，晓得什么！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（家院上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "棺匣到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俱已抬到午门候旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（家院、夫人同下。万历、内监同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙爱卿，孤命你回府，造来棺匣，可怎么样了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣棺匣已到，万岁过目。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "内臣观看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "内监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "内监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀万岁：察来察去，察了一十九口。内有一口，长余一尺，宽余七寸，二龙"
        },
        {
          "character": "内监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "戏珠，黄纱罩顶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一孙安，孤命你造来一十八口棺匣，你为何造来一十九口。内有一口，长余"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一尺，宽余七寸，二龙戏珠，黄纱罩顶。是何道理？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁依为臣本奏，还在罢了。若要不肯，小昏王你就丧在这口棺匣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一孙安，上的殿来，渺视寡人，哪里容得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金瓜武士，推出午门，与我开刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐彦昭、杨溥、马子千、杨太同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐彦昭、杨溥、马子千、杨太",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刀下留人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐彦昭、杨溥、马子千、杨太",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁，孙安只可一饶，不可一斩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗，孙安上殿。渺视寡人，再要保本，一例问罪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐彦昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐彦昭",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "在此金殿用目睁，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐彦昭",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "倒叫某家喜心中。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐彦昭",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "只怕江山不太平。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐彦昭",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我今要打主圣龙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐彦昭",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我今不打万历主"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐彦昭",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我把铜锤拿在手"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徐千岁慢着，小王不斩孙安，也就是了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "内臣替朕传旨，孙安上殿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "内监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "内监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "圣旨下：孙安上殿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只说法场死，不想又复生。来在金殿上，大骂无道龙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈，好一昏王。将我绑下殿去，为何不杀，又不斩？"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一孙安，上的殿来，大骂小王，哪里容得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金瓜武士，推出午门，与我问斩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好孙安为何大笑。放回来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小昏王，将我三番两次，绑下金殿，为何不杀，是何道理？"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一孙安，为何发笑？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一小昏王，不记得当年老王晏驾，把江山托与李良执掌。谁想那李良，昧透"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "血心，要夺大明江山。那时多亏徐千岁、杨大人，保你小昏王，七岁上登基。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自你登基以来，酒色昏迷，国事不正，难以坐朝，不听我忠臣本奏，听信谗言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那张居正用本保就，听信他的谗言，你就封他掌朝一个太师。小昏王似你思"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前想后。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一孙安，上的殿来，你敢说孤王听信谗言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金瓜武士，推出午门斩首。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐彦昭、杨溥、马子千、杨太",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刀下留人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐彦昭、杨溥、马子千、杨太",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁，孙安只可一饶，不可一斩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗！好一孙安，上的殿来，大骂小王，身犯国家王律，定斩不容。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐彦昭",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一见孙安绑下殿，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐彦昭",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "好不叫人心痛酸。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐彦昭",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "收心务本种庄田。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐彦昭",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "职都押在龙书案"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨溥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨溥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "职都押在龙书案"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨溥",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一见千岁下金殿，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨溥",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "倒叫杨溥泪不干。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨溥",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "山西蒲州快乐安然。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨溥",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "职都押在龙书案"
        },
        {
          "character": "马子千",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "众位大人下金殿，"
        },
        {
          "character": "马子千",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "倒叫下官不耐烦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马子千",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "收心务本不居官。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马子千",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "职都押在龙书案"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨太",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "众位大人把殿下，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨太",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "倒叫杨太泪汪汪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨太",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "捎代拣棉花。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张居正上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张居正",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "满朝文武俱下殿，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张居正",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "留我一人保江山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "内监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众位大人下殿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "替朕传旨，孙安上殿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "接旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣谢过我主不斩之恩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非是小王不斩与你，多亏众位大人保本。孙爱卿，寡人有心，发你边外居官，"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "琢磨琢磨你的性体，小王自有搬运回朝之日。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同使眼色，过场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣我愿去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "愿去就好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "内臣看了地理图。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "在金殿献地图用目观看，"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你听小王对你言："
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "上写着云南道居官不浅"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个么，臣我不去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "四川城内去居官。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个么，臣我还是不去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "湖北居官路长远，"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你到那里把民安。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个么，臣我还是不去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "这不好来那不好，"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "荆州二府去坐官。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个么，臣我愿去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎说愿去，就好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣我还是不去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你怎么不去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "荆州乡绅太多呀，将为臣勘磨死，也是有的。为臣还是不去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎说将你勘磨死，也是有的。小王恩赐二十四杆红油漆棍，打死豪恶之家，绝"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "棍一条。若要使净，回京再领。你去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣我还是不去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你怎么又不去了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣我出京时节，众家大臣，手扶轿杆，大喊三声，法官到任来也。臣我还要威"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "武威武。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你在金殿骂小王，你还要怎样威武？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣我为国尽忠。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "件件依从。你去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在金殿叩了头圣恩来谢，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我只得在金殿用目细观。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我只得官到那边。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徐千岁你过来臣有话言："
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "把江山让与了李良贼担。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他封了昭阳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打碎了金锁三道栓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨国相请过来臣有话言："
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他倒说徐、杨是邪奸。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多亏了徐、杨执掌江山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒色昏迷难把朝全。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他反道妄信邪奸。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马恩师请过了弟子有言："
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来往书信要你传。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恩师你与弟子大报冤仇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨大人请过来臣有话言："
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "南创北杀保主江山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小功劳也有万万千。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙安",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "八大朝臣十二连官，一个一个，且都免见。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙安下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "万历",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众卿，孙爱卿出京，小王心中不悦，众卿回府。"
        },
        {
          "character": "内监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请驾回宫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
